## üöÄ Key Features

- **Intelligent Google Drive Integration** ‚Äî automatically creates structured folder hierarchies for each event and syncs photos without manual file management
- **AI-Powered Photo Search** ‚Äî built unique OCR pipeline that extracts text from images and enables keyword-based photo discovery across entire photo libraries
- **Professional Client Portals** ‚Äî white-label public galleries with customizable branding that photographers share directly with clients for photo selection and download
- **Real-time Event Management** ‚Äî live progress tracking showing upload status, OCR processing, and photo counts across ongoing events
- **Zero-Dependency Hosting** ‚Äî engineered split-architecture that overcomes Vercel timeout limits by processing OCR externally while maintaining single-tenant deployment simplicity

